ministered with a moderate inhibitor of CYP450 3A4.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/167256/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Ethotoin, Rufinamide, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Ganaxolone, More', 'Mometasone furoate, Umeclidinium, Aclidinium, Glycopyrronium, Flunisolide, Ipratropium, Cromoglicic acid, Revefenacin, Nedocromil, Tiotropium, Beclomethasone dipropionate, More', 1767369485);
